<p><hi rend='Bold'>Othondokua</hi>. <foreign>Betoine (betonica, btonica officinalis)</foreign><mentioned><SUP> [93]</SUP></mentioned><foreign>.</foreign></p>
<p><hi rend='Bold'>Papantzea</hi>. <foreign>Pens&eacute;e (pensamiento).</foreign></p>
<p>Tizanak sendotzen d&uuml;t&uuml; haurren urtheminak.</p>
<p><hi rend='Bold'>Parietera</hi>. <foreign>Parietaire (pelosilla, parietaria difusa)</foreign><mentioned><SUP> [94]</SUP></mentioned></p>
